<div class="min-h-screen w-full overflow-auto bg-stone-50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-md">

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">

        <% if flash[:notice] %>
            <div class="mt-5 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 p-3 text-sm text-emerald-700">
            <%= flash[:notice] %>
            </div>
        <% end %>
      <div class ="text-center">
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">メッセージ投稿完了</h1>

        <p class="mt-3 text-sl text-stone-600">
          <span class="font-semibold text-stone-700"><%= @celebration.receiver_name %></span>さんへの
          メッセージを受け付けました。
        </p>

      <div class="py-8">
          <%= image_tag "icon_sendingletter.png",class: "mx-auto w-24 sm:w-28 opacity-95" %>
      </div>

        <div class="mt-5 border-t border-stone-200 pt-6 text-left">
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-center text-stone-500">
            このページのURLを共有すると、他の人もメッセージを送れます。
          </p>

          <div class="mt-3 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 bg-stone-50 p-3 text-xs text-center text-stone-700 break-all">
            <%= "#{request.base_url}/l/#{@celebration.share_url}" %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
          <%= link_to "もう一通送る",
                "/l/#{@celebration.share_url}",
                class: "block w-full rounded-xl bg-teal-700 px-6 py-3 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-[0_4px_0_#115e59] transition-all duration-150 hover:bg-teal-600 active:translate-y-[3px] active:scale-[0.98] active:shadow-none" %>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 flex justify-center">
            <% if logged_in? %>
            <%= link_to "画面を閉じる",edit_celebration_path(@celebration),
                  class: "block w-full rounded-xl border border-stone-300 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 hover:bg-stone-50" %>
            <% else %>
            <%= link_to "画面を閉じる",root_path,
                  class: "block w-full rounded-xl border border-stone-300 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 hover:bg-stone-50" %>
            <% end %>
        </div>

          <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-stone-500">
            作成者が内容を確定すると、お祝いページで閲覧できるようになります。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
